'''史蒂芬·克拉布'''（{{lang-en|Stephen Crabb}}；{{bd|1973年|1月20日||catIdx=T}}），是威爾斯[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]黨員與自2005年起的[[英國國會|英國國會]][[普里塞里-彭布羅克郡_(英國國會選區)|普里塞里-彭布羅克郡選區]][[國會議員|下議院議員]]，在2014年7月15日，他獲委任為[[威爾斯事務大臣|威爾斯事務大臣]]<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-19495871 | work=BBC News | title=MP Stephen Crabb wins Wales Office promotion | date=5 September 2012 | accessdate=2015-05-22 | archive-date=2016-01-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160111071447/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-19495871 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾是一位[[黨鞭|黨鞭]]和威爾士大臣<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-19495797 | work=BBC News | title=The reshuffle: twist in the tail | date=5 September 2012 | accessdate=2015-05-22 | archive-date=2016-03-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325082916/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-19495797 | dead-url=no }}</ref>；BBC描述他曾擁有同時作為黨鞭及大臣的不尋常雙重角色<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-19497621 | work=BBC News | title=The unexpected Wales Office call for Baroness Randerson | date=5 September 2012 | accessdate=2015-05-22 | archive-date=2014-09-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911013736/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-19497621 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-19499236 | work=BBC News | title=Stephen Crabb MP on his new job in Wales Office | date=6 September 2012 | accessdate=2015-05-22 | archive-date=2016-01-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160111071447/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-19499236 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年，[[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]辭任首相和保守黨黨魁職位，觸發[[2016年英國保守黨黨魁選舉|保守黨黨魁選舉]]。史蒂芬·克拉布宣布競逐<ref name="CrabbTeam">{{cite web|url=http://www.politico.eu/article/work-and-pensions-secretary-stephen-crabb-declares-he-is-running-to-replace-david-cameron-as-conservative-party-leader/|title=Stephen Crabb declares he is running to replace David Cameron|publisher=[[Politico_Europe|Politico Europe]]|last=McTague|first=Tom|date=28 June 2016|accessdate=2016-07-07|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629175157/http://www.politico.eu/article/work-and-pensions-secretary-stephen-crabb-declares-he-is-running-to-replace-david-cameron-as-conservative-party-leader/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在第一輪投票中排名尾二，決定退選並在決勝局中支持[[文翠珊|文翠珊]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/politics/conservative-party-leadership-race-stephen-crabb-pulls-out-of-contest-to-leave-threehorse-race-a3288791.html|title=Stephen Crabb pulls out of Tory leadership contest|newspaper=Evening Standard|accessdate=2017-12-04|language=en-GB|archive-date=2016-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160705202320/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/politics/conservative-party-leadership-race-stephen-crabb-pulls-out-of-contest-to-leave-threehorse-race-a3288791.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==谴责中国政府==
2020年9月8日在[[英国工党|工党]][[希柏恩·麦克唐纳|希柏恩·麦克唐纳]]的协调下，与包括[[英国保守党|英国保守党]]外交事务委员会主席[[托马斯·图根达特|托马斯·图根达特]]、[[自由民主党_(英国)|自由民主党]]领袖[[爱德·戴维|爱德·戴维]]，以及{{le|英国绿党|Green Party (UK)}}、[[苏格兰民族党|苏格兰民族党]]和[[威尔士党|威尔士党]]在内的130多名议员给中国驻英大使[[刘晓明|刘晓明]]写信，联名谴责中国政府[[新疆再教育营|针对新疆维吾尔穆斯林的行为]]。<ref>{{cite news |author1=法广 |title=英国近百名议员联名谴责中共针对新疆维吾尔穆斯林的行为 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200909-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%E8%81%94%E5%90%8D%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA |accessdate=2020-09-29 |agency=RFI |date=2020-09-10 |archive-date=2020-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910225118/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200909-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%E8%81%94%E5%90%8D%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E5%90%BE%E5%B0%94%E7%A9%86%E6%96%AF%E6%9E%97%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=DAVID ALTON |title=Led by Siobhain McDonagh MP, 130 parliamentarians have today written to the Chinese Ambassador to the UK condemning treatment of Uyghur people in Xinjiang |url=https://davidalton.net/2020/09/08/led-by-siobhain-mcdonagh-mp-130-parliamentarians-have-today-written-to-the-chinese-ambassador-to-the-uk-condemning-treatment-of-uyghur-people-in-xinjiang/ |accessdate=2020-09-29 |date=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917001800/https://davidalton.net/2020/09/08/led-by-siobhain-mcdonagh-mp-130-parliamentarians-have-today-written-to-the-chinese-ambassador-to-the-uk-condemning-treatment-of-uyghur-people-in-xinjiang/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

